RECITALS
--------
WHEREAS, Developer has created and developed a website software application for educational institution management; and
WHEREAS, Client desires to obtain a license to use said software for their educational institution operations; and
WHEREAS, the Parties wish to set forth the terms and conditions of such license;

NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants and agreements contained herein, the Parties agree as follows:

1. PROJECT DETAILS AND SPECIFICATIONS
-------------------------------------
1.1 Project Name: Jharkhand Public School Website
1.2 Description: A comprehensive school website with content management capabilities designed for educational institution operations and public information dissemination
1.3 Technology Stack: Next.js 15.4.1, React 19.1.0, TypeScript 5.0, Tailwind CSS 4.0
1.4 Delivery Date: August 1, 2025
1.5 Version: 1.0.0
1.6 Domain: https://jpsbarharwa.in

