10.2 Upon termination, Client shall cease all use of the Software and destroy all copies in their possession, except for the deployed production version which may continue to operate under the terms existing at termination.

10.3 Sections 4 (Intellectual Property), 7 (Warranties), 8 (Limitation of LIABILITY), 9 (Indemnification), and 11 (General Provisions) shall survive termination.

